OL,6,FTrevor Sorbie died "peacefully"
OL,7,Falongside his family and beloved dog
OL,8,Fat his side on Friday, as ITV News'
OL,9,FCari Davies reports
OL,11,FCelebrity hairdresser Trevor Sorbie
OL,12,Fhas died aged 75, his company has
OL,13,Fannounced.
OL,15,FThe Scottish stylist gained fame after
OL,16,Fhis creation of the wedge cut,
OL,17,Falongside his TV appearances. Sorbie
OL,18,Fwas known for cutting the hair of the
OL,19,Frich and famous including Grace Jones,
OL,20,FThe Beach Boys and Dame Helen Mirren.
