OL,3,CCelebrity hairdresser Trevor Sorbie
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FIn October, he revealed he had weeks
OL,7,Fto live after his bowel cancer had
OL,8,Fspread to his liver. Speaking on ITV's
OL,9,FThis Morning, he said his surgeon
OL,10,Fwould no longer operate as it was too
OL,11,Fclose to a major blood vessel.
OL,13,FHe died "peacefully" alongside his
OL,14,Ffamily and beloved dog at his side.
OL,16,FHis company announced the news of his
OL,17,Fdeath on Instagram. A post said: "It
OL,18,Fis with heartfelt emotion that we
OL,19,Fshare the passing of our esteemed
OL,20,Ffounder, Trevor Sorbie MBE.
