OL,3,CCelebrity hairdresser Trevor Sorbie
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,F"Trevor passed away peacefully with
OL,7,Fhis family and beloved dog by his
OL,8,Fside. Trevor's journey, marked by
OL,9,Funparalleled creativity and kindness,
OL,10,Fhas left an indelible mark on the
OL,11,Fworld of hairdressing and beyond...
OL,13,F"Honouring Trevor's wishes, there will
OL,14,Fbe no funeral. In lieu of flowers, we
OL,15,Finvite you to support four charities:
OL,16,FMarie Curie, Cancer Research UK,
OL,17,FRowans Hospice and My New Hair, all
OL,18,Fclose to his heart.
