OL,6,FThe award-winning stylist previously
OL,7,Fset up the charity, My New Hair, to
OL,8,Fprovide "public advice and support a
OL,9,Fnational network of independent salons
OL,10,Fand professionals who provide a wig
OL,11,Fstyling service for people suffering
OL,12,Ffrom cancer and medical hair loss".
OL,14,FIn 2018, he launched a free wig
OL,15,Fcustomisation service for NHS patients
OL,16,Fwho have experienced medical hair
OL,17,Floss, including those undergoing
OL,18,Fchemotherapy, at his home through My
OL,19,FNew Hair.
