OL,6,FSorbie was a four-time British
OL,7,FHairdresser of the Year winner and his
OL,8,Fmethods helped to transform the world
OL,9,Fof hairdressing through trend-setting
OL,10,Fstyles such as the wolf man,
OL,11,Fsculpture, and the wave ` and a fast-
OL,12,Fdrying process called the scrunch.
