OL,3,CCelebrity hairdresser Trevor Sorbie
OL,4,Cdies aged 75
OL,6,FBorn in Paisley, Scotland, on March 13
OL,7,F1949, his family later moved to
OL,8,FEngland where Sorbie was bullied at
OL,9,Fschool, leading him to drop out as a
OL,10,Fteenager when he began as an
OL,11,Fapprentice in his father's barber shop.
OL,13,FIn 1979 he opened the first Trevor
OL,14,FSorbie salon in Covent Garden, London,
OL,15,Fwith the company going on to open
OL,16,Flocations in Brighton, Bristol,
OL,17,FHampstead, Manchester and Richmond.
